## Troubleshooting

### Server not appearing in Claude

1. Check the config file path is correct
2. Verify JSON syntax: `cat ~/Library/Application\ Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json | jq .`
3. Ensure the path to index.js is absolute

### "Module not found" errors

```bash
npm run build
# Verify dist/server/index.js exists
ls dist/server/
```

### Permission errors

Check the permissions declared in manifest.json match what the server actually needs.

### Server crashes on startup

```bash
# Run manually to see errors
node dist/server/index.js
```

